INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff8080815157d84b015157fc331b002c', 'Main business sphere', '2015-11-30 18:42:04', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>R&amp;D on national special subjects, R&amp;D oncoal-to-oil technology, industrialized technology transfer, training and consulting, catalyst production and sales, R&amp;D of special coal-to-oil equipment, chemical engineering design for energy and coal, EPC, construction management and other business, coal-to-oil technical support and service for customers at home and abroad.</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137ab01c60005', '6', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff8080815157d84b015157f99e5d0027', 'Founding and personnel', '2015-11-30 18:39:15', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>SYNFUELS China Co., Ltd. was registered and established in April, 2006. There are more than 900 employees in the company, including over 80% engineers, designers and technical researchers. There are 47 employees of PHD degree or above, 203 employees of Master degree, 18 researchers and professor-level senior engineers, 139 vice researchers and senior engineers.</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137ab01c60005', '5', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff8080815157d84b015157fccb41002e', 'Function allocation', '2015-11-30 18:42:43', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>The company has three major R&amp;D bases in Beijing, Inner Mongolia and Taiyuan, forming the industrial supporting platform of SYNFULES China in basic research, engineering design, technical development, project industrialization and seamless matching of domestic large equipmentproduction. It supports the development, promotion and application of independent technology, joins international patent system construction in international technology market and forms a systematic technical supporting system for large-scale coal-to-oil industry.<span lang=\"EN-US\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137ab01c60005', '7', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff8080815157d84b015157fd39cf0030', 'The industrialization process', '2015-11-30 18:43:11', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>Based on the independent intellectual rights and technology of SYNFUELS China, the coal-to-synthetic-oil demonstrative project withannual output 160 thousand tons ofInner Mongolia Yitai Group started to be built in May, 2006.The pilot run was successful in March, 2009. Based on the independent intellectual rights and technology of SYNFUELS China, the indirect coal liquefaction industrial demonstrative project of annual output 160 thousand tons built by Shanxi Luan Mines Group succeeded in the feeding pilot run in July, 2009. Qualified oil product has been produced.<br />\r\nIn July, 2010, CIECC organized Chinese experts to check the performance of the Yitaicoal-to- oil demonstrative project with annual output of 160 thousand tons. The expert group reached conclusion after evaluation: the coal-to-oil catalyst, reactor and composition technology developed by SYNFUELS China totally reached the expected goals. It has the technical conditions to design and constructcoal-to-oil project of million-ton level. It marked China&rsquo;s independent, advanced and reliable coal-to-oil industrial technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 28pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137ab01c60005', '2', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff8080815157d84b015157fdb4000032', 'Achievements', '2015-11-30 18:43:43', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>Due to the breakthroughs the company has made in coal-to-oil industrialized technology, it has won many awards such as the Outstanding Technological Achievement Award by the Chinese Academy of Sciences and the First Prize of National Energy Technological Advancement by National Energy Administration. In 2014, National Energy Administration established the &ldquo;National energy R&amp;D center on coal-based liquid fuel&rdquo; in SYNFUELS China. The &ldquo;Beijing key lab of clean coal-based liquid fuel&rdquo; was accepted by Beijing Municipal Science and Technology Committee.<span lang=\"EN-US\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137ab01c60005', '3', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff8080815157d84b015157fe4a190034', 'Development direction', '2015-11-30 18:44:21', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>Based on the successful operation of the demonstrative project with annual output of 160 thousand tons, SYNFUELS China is working on the commercialized coal-to-oil projects: Shenhua Ningxia Coal project with yearly output of 4 million tons, Shanxi Luan project with yearly output of 1 million tons and Inner Mongolia Yitai project with yearly output of 1.2 million tons. After production is launched in these projects, Chinese technology and industry onindirect coal liquefaction certainly would rank among the tops in the world.<br />\r\nNext the company shall connect processing of sub-bituminous coal and bituminous coal on the basis of technical development in grading liquidation and processing lignite. Then industrial demonstration can be made. The Chinese grading liquidation technology of hydrogenation coal-to-oil and grading liquidation technology of residue gasification to synthetic oil shall take a leading role in world coal energy conversion field. China shall have absolute advantages in technological industrialization in world coal liquidation industry market.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" mso-bidi-language:=\"\" mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\"><!--[endif]--></span></body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137ab01c60005', '4', '1', '', '', '');
