INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ca5a22f0142', 'In 2009', '2015-12-01 16:25:37', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">-In March, 0.16 million tons/year coal based synthetic oil industrial demonstration project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Group, which was built by using Synfuels China technology, realized a success driving and smoothly produced oil.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">-In May, Professor Li Yongwang, general manager of the Company, won 2009 Annual National May 1 Labor Medal.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">- In July, 0.16 million tons/year coal indirect liquefaction demonstration project of Shanxi Lu&rsquo;an Mining Group, which was built by using Synfuels China independent IPR, realized a successful commissioning and produced qualified products.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\