INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b4dd2b10015', '', '2015-12-01 10:10:05', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">In&nbsp;order&nbsp;to&nbsp;speed&nbsp;up&nbsp;large-scale&nbsp;industrialization&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal&nbsp;based&nbsp;synthetic&nbsp;oil&nbsp;project&nbsp;and&nbsp;&nbsp;transform&nbsp;scientific&nbsp;and&nbsp;technological&nbsp;achievements&nbsp;into&nbsp;practical&nbsp;productive&nbsp;forces,&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;actively&nbsp;carries&nbsp;out&nbsp;the&nbsp;coal&nbsp;based&nbsp;synthetic&nbsp;oil&nbsp;technology&nbsp;industrialization&nbsp;construction,&nbsp;and&nbsp;&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;time,&nbsp;it&nbsp;keeps&nbsp;high&nbsp;starting&nbsp;point,&nbsp;sustainability&nbsp;and&nbsp;scale&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;independent&nbsp;technology.&nbsp;In&nbsp;September&nbsp;2006,&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;registered&nbsp;a&nbsp;wholly-owned&nbsp;subsidiary&nbsp;in&nbsp;Beijing-&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;Engineering</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Holdings&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;(referred&nbsp;to&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company)&nbsp;to&nbsp;facilitate&nbsp;the&nbsp;seamless&nbsp;connection&nbsp;between&nbsp;technical&nbsp;pilot&nbsp;test&nbsp;in&nbsp;laboratory&nbsp;and&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;technology&nbsp;development&nbsp;process.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">The&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;moved&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;office&nbsp;building&nbsp;of&nbsp;Naner&nbsp;Street&nbsp;of&nbsp;Huairou&nbsp;District&nbsp;Yanqi&nbsp;Economic&nbsp;Development&nbsp;Zone&nbsp;C,&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;city&nbsp;in&nbsp;March&nbsp;2011.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Based&nbsp;on&nbsp;overall&nbsp;technology&nbsp;and&nbsp;R&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;D&nbsp;capability&nbsp;of&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;mainly&nbsp;engages&nbsp;in&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;design,&nbsp;EPC&nbsp;general&nbsp;contracting,&nbsp;project&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;services,&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;survey,&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;consulting,&nbsp;technology&nbsp;development,&nbsp;training&nbsp;and&nbsp;consulting,&nbsp;technology&nbsp;services,&nbsp;R&amp;D&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal&nbsp;chemical&nbsp;industry&nbsp;and&nbsp;coal-to-oil&nbsp;proprietary&nbsp;equipment,&nbsp;environmental&nbsp;evaluation&nbsp;of&nbsp;energy&nbsp;and&nbsp;chemical&nbsp;engineering,&nbsp;project&nbsp;bidding,&nbsp;technology&nbsp;import&nbsp;and&nbsp;export&nbsp;and&nbsp;agent&nbsp;business&nbsp;of&nbsp;import&nbsp;and&nbsp;export.&nbsp;Since&nbsp;its&nbsp;founding,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;considers&nbsp;&ldquo;Our&nbsp;Expertise,&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;in&nbsp;Future&rdquo;&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;principle&nbsp;and&nbsp;&ldquo;&nbsp;Leading&nbsp;in&nbsp;Science&nbsp;and&nbsp;Technology&nbsp;to&nbsp;Ensure&nbsp;National&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;Strategy&nbsp;Security&rdquo;&nbsp;as&nbsp;its&nbsp;own&nbsp;duty.&nbsp;Carrying&nbsp;out&nbsp;work&nbsp;with&nbsp;great&nbsp;efforts,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;was&nbsp;named&nbsp;the&nbsp;&ldquo;Diamond&nbsp;Company&nbsp;of&nbsp;Tsinghua&nbsp;Science&nbsp;Park&rdquo;&nbsp;in&nbsp;2008&nbsp;,&nbsp;and&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;year,&nbsp;it&nbsp;was&nbsp;named&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;&ldquo;100&nbsp;National&nbsp;Pilot&nbsp;Innovative&nbsp;Enterprises&rdquo;&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;was&nbsp;approved&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;High-tech&nbsp;Enterprise&nbsp;by&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Municipal&nbsp;Science&nbsp;and&nbsp;Technology&nbsp;Commission,&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Municipal&nbsp;Finance&nbsp;Bureau,&nbsp;State&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;of&nbsp;Taxation&nbsp;and&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Municipal&nbsp;Local&nbsp;Taxation&nbsp;Bureau.&nbsp;Due&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;effective&nbsp;time&nbsp;limit&nbsp;stipulated&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;high-tech&nbsp;certification,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;in&nbsp;2014&nbsp;to&nbsp;reapplied&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;successfully&nbsp;obtained&nbsp;the&nbsp;approval.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">The&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;full&nbsp;absorps&nbsp;management&nbsp;experience&nbsp;of&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;and&nbsp;foreign&nbsp;famous&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;companies&nbsp;and&nbsp;invests&nbsp;heavily&nbsp;in&nbsp;building&nbsp;the&nbsp;infrastructure&nbsp;which&nbsp;consistent&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;international&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;company,&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;time,&nbsp;makes&nbsp;full&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;advantage&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;system&nbsp;and&nbsp;mechanism,&nbsp;setting&nbsp;up&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;technical&nbsp;team&nbsp;and&nbsp;management&nbsp;team&nbsp;which&nbsp;was&nbsp;organized&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;famous&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;company&nbsp;participating&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;construction&nbsp;of&nbsp;large-scale&nbsp;oil&nbsp;refining,&nbsp;chemistry,&nbsp;medicine,&nbsp;municipal&nbsp;work&nbsp;and&nbsp;environmen&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;and&nbsp;with&nbsp;experienced&nbsp;talents;&nbsp;the&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Company&nbsp;also&nbsp;establishes&nbsp;advanced&nbsp;management&nbsp;system,&nbsp;develops&nbsp;a&nbsp;long-term&nbsp;talent&nbsp;incentive&nbsp;mechanism&nbsp;and&nbsp;further&nbsp;creates&nbsp;the&nbsp;scientific,&nbsp;advanced,&nbsp;standardized&nbsp;and&nbsp;rational&nbsp;enterprise&nbsp;culture;&nbsp;In&nbsp;addition,&nbsp;its&nbsp;target,&nbsp;ability&nbsp;and&nbsp;ideas&nbsp;are&nbsp;constantly&nbsp;heading&nbsp;forwar&nbsp;to&nbsp;internationa&nbsp;professional&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;company.</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137af3cb8001e', '2', '2', '', '', '');
