INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515cf203e4026c', 'hydrate technology', '2015-12-01 17:49:03', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>Regarding the hydrate Water Treatment Process, Synfuels China utilizes the characteristics that some small molecule gas and water can produce hydrate at a certain temperature and pressure conditions so as to achieve the purpose of separating wastewater and impurities in the water. The process is that the wastewater contacts the cryogenic small molecules substance after cooling and produces hydrate and concentrated solution in a specific device, achieving the solid-liquid separation. In another device, hydrate structure is destroyed to regenerate high purity water and small molecular gas. Part concentrated solution mixes with feedstock, the other part is exhausted out of the system to accept further processing through other processes.</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513838ea9b00b2', '1', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b7707a5004b', 'Fischer-tropsch synthesis catalyst products', '2015-12-01 10:55:06', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">The catalyst technology of Synfuels China involves in the research on catalytic and process chemistry of converting indirectly syngas into liquid fuel (GTL) including the preparation of chemical catalysts, catalytic reaction engineering, engineering base of catalyst preparation, catalyst design and optimization theory, the relationship between catalyst microstructure and performance, the detailed analysis on the stability and activity as well as selectivity of catalyst in the reaction process, catalytic reaction kinetics and mechanisms, development of new catalyst system and catalytic materials etc. Currently, based on the research on the systematic and solid foundation and theoretical calculation as well as essential recognition of FTS (Fischer-Tropsch synthesis) reaction process, we re-design and develop, from the atomic scale, a series of FTS catalysts including high temperature, low temperature, heavy hydrocarbons and olefins-rich series.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company has successfully developed the processing technology of low-temperature slurry-bed Fischer-tropsch synthesis and original high-temperature slurry-bed Fischer-tropsch synthesis, which are based around the technology ofFischer-tropsch catalysts. The production equipment for Fischer-tropsch synthesis catalysts with yearly output of 150 million tons in Huainan Catalyst Co., Ltd. of SYNFUELS has been constructed and completed. The Fischer-tropsch synthesis catalysts produced there have been successfully applied to the coal-to-oil industrial demonstrative factories in Inner Mongolia Yitai Group and Shanxi Luan Group, which has yearly output of 160 thousand tons. Fisher-tropsch synthesis catalyst factory with yearly output of12 thousand tons was built to support the commercialized factory with yearly output of millions of tons. The high-temperature, low-temperature, heavy hydrocarbonsand rich olefinseries of Fischer-tropsch synthesis catalysts are redesigned on atomic level.<o:p></o:p><span lang=\"EN-US\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383ba99800ca', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/proSer-ltBg.png', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d3d83b90376', '煤制油行业首次拥有国家标准 我公司拔得头筹', '2015-12-01 19:11:31', '2011年1月13日，煤基费托合成检测方法国家标准审查会在北京召开。会上，由中科合成油技术有限公司、煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室牵头制定的煤炭间接液化过程中的两项分析方法国家标准：《煤基费托合成原料气中H2、N2、CO、CO2和CH4的测定—气相色谱法》和《煤基费托合成尾气中H2、N2、CO、CO2和C1～C8烃的测定—气相色谱法》通过专家组审查，即将由国家标准化管理委员会发布实施。这是公司煤间接液化合成油技术继示范厂成功应用后的又一重大突破，体现出公司分析方法的可靠性和权威性，奠定了公司在煤制油领域的地位和引领作用。\r\n \r\n2006年，公司向国家标准委员会提交了两项国家标准草案和项目建议书，通过申报、专家评审、答辩与择优录取等一系列程序后，国家标准委员会于2008年下达了综合[2008]154号和168号文件，委托中科合成油技术有限公司、煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室为上述两项国家标准的制定负责单位，项目编号为20083262-T-603和20081494-T-603。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b8c3470052', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/bztp(1).jpg', '2011-1-13');
