INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d43965f039a', '我公司李永旺总经理参加谋跨越促转型劳模事迹报告', '2015-12-01 19:18:09', '2010年9月13日，“谋跨越促转型劳模事迹报告会”在山西省太原工人文化宫举行，省委副书记、省政协主席薛延忠出席报告会并会见劳模代表，省人大常委会副主任、省总工会主席郭海亮主持报告会并作总结讲话。山西省劳动竞赛委员会成员单位领导，省总工会领导，各市总工会、各省级产业工会（工委）负责人及经济技术部部长，省总机关全体干部、省总直属事业单位副处级以上干部，以及省直机关、省城企业劳模和职工代表等1000多人参加报告会。我公司李永旺总经理作为4名劳动模范代表之一参加了大会。\r\n \r\n省模范单位代表、中共右玉县委书记陈小洪，全国劳模、全国知识型职工标兵、山西柴油机有限公司高级技师金长福，全国劳模、山西潞安集团董事长任润厚，全国先进工作者、中科院山西煤炭化学研究所研究员李永旺分别作了题为《“不毛之地”是怎样变成“塞上绿洲”的》、《用精神和知识托起转型跨越》、《抢抓机遇，放胆争先，努力当好全省转型跨越发展的排头兵》和《做科技创新带头人，为转型跨越作贡献》的报告。\r\n \r\n李永旺总经理在报告中谈到，山西作为煤炭资源大省，在工业经济发展过程中，煤、焦、冶、电四大支柱产业占80%，存在着高消耗，高污染等问题。当前，我省正处于负重赶超的关键时期，机不可失，不进则退，要成功实现转型跨越，离不开高科技的支撑。正是由于国内丰富的煤炭资源优势，煤制油技术具有广阔的发展前景，特别是随着国际石油价格的攀升和能源需求的不断加大，以及科学的不断进步,这种安全、高效、清洁、环保的煤制油技术在中国的经济社会发展，乃至世界经济发展中的重大作用将会逐渐凸显出来，从而发挥巨大的作用。\r\n \r\n在全省上下凝心聚力加快转型发展跨越发展的重要时刻，举行这场劳模事迹报告会，大力弘扬工人阶级伟大品格，用劳模的先进事迹感召人民群众，用劳模的优秀品质引领社会风尚，在全社会营造劳动光荣、知识崇高、人才宝贵、创造伟大的社会氛围，对激励和鼓舞全省广大职工和劳动群众充分发挥主力军作用，对努力实现山西科学发展的宏伟蓝图具有十分重要的意义.（综合部 董琳）', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '1', '1', '', '', '2010-9-13');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b8f1ed80066', 'Lu’an Coal-based Synthetic Oil Demonstration Project', '2015-12-01 11:21:24', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Based on coal-based liquid fuel synthesis slurry bed industrialized technology, independently researched and developed by Synfuels China Technology Co., Ltd., Shanxi Lu&rsquo;an coal-based synthetic oil demonstration project is a continuation of the national high-tech projects and major CAS Knowledge Innovation Project, constructed by Shanxi Lu&rsquo;an coal-based synthetic oil company, which is wholly owned byShanxi Lu&#39; an Mining Group Co., Ltd. Shanxi Lu&rsquo;an Group is a national large coal production base in China, ranking the 176 in the Top-500 enterprises, and it is one of the five Coal Groups in Shanxi Province.Lu&rsquo;an coal-based synthetic oil demonstration project is located in Lu&rsquo;an Group&rsquo;s Tunliu Coal-to- oil Recycling Economy Park. The Park bases on 0.16 million tons/year of coal-based synthetic oil demonstration project and constructs coal oil industry in two phases, 3 million tons of coal-oil device in the first phase and 2 million tons in the second phase.Eventually, it will be gradually developed into Coal-to- oil Recycling Economy Park centered around 5.4 million tons/year of coal-based synthetic oil project, matched with coal mines, coal preparation plant, fertilizer plants, oil plants, tar processing plants, wastewater treatment plants and other projects.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383d9d8900d7', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/lasf_1.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b8fdbed006b', '', '2015-12-01 11:22:13', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Lu&rsquo; an coal-based synthetic oil project can produce 160,000 tons synthetic oil annually, including 30,000 tons of LPG and naphtha, and 100,000 tons of high-class diesel, whose cetane reaches 74.8 and meet Euro V emissions standards. The project includes: air separation plant, a coal pressurized gasification plant, gas purification devices, Fischer-Tropsch synthesis and oil refining plant, tail gas treatment unit, 60,000KW gas and steam turbine (IGCC), and supporting public works equipment and facilities. With the total investment of RMB 3.2 billion, it cogenerates 180,000 tons of synthetic ammonia, and 300,000 tons of urea, thereby realizing oil-cogeneration and reducing 270,000 tons of carbon dioxide emissions.Demonstration projects of Lu&rsquo;an coal based synthetic oil officially launched in February 2006, which had been approved for construction by development and reform commission of Shanxi province. The project completed its feasibility study report writing in 2006 July. In the end of 2006, it completed the process of Fischer Tropsch synthesis system package design. In 2007 June, it completed the basic design of Fischer Tropsch synthesis system. In 2007 August, It began to design in detail, and step by step started into the areas of equipment procurement and construction, as well.<br />\r\nIn July 7, 2009, the core of Fischer Tropsch synthesis reaction device of Lu&rsquo;an demonstration projects started to load catalyst. After more than 70 hours of test running, it successfully produced high quality oil. The successful operation of the demonstration project fully illustrated that the catalyst, reactor and synthesis technology researched and developed independently by Zhongke synthetic oil Technology Company completely reached the international leading level.<br />\r\nThe success of the project operation promotes the countries and Shanxi province to actively implement the adjustment of industrial structure, change the mode of economic growth and to realize the development of diversified energy structure.Consequently, it plays an important role in promoting the implementation of the national energy strategy, accelerating the transformation of Shanxi province from coal heartland into chemical industrial zone and speeding up the new energy and industrial base construction.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383d9d8900d7', '2', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/lasf_2.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d446b38039c', '', '2015-12-01 19:19:03', '2010年8月25日至27日，2010年中国国际煤化工展览会、中国国际煤化工发展论坛在北京国家会议中心隆重召开。此次展览会及发展论坛由中国石油和化学工业联合会、中国煤炭工业协会主办，国家化工行业生产力促进中心、中国国际贸易促进委员会化工行业分会协办，是全球首次以煤化工为主题的展览会及发展论坛。中科合成油技术有限公司作为国内拥有完全自主知识产权的煤炭间接液化技术研发代表，受邀参展并出席了以煤制油、煤基多联产及低碳技术创新与发展为主题的分论坛。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/IMG_1942.JPG', '2010-8-25');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d45d10e03a6', '', '2015-12-01 19:20:35', '通过参加本届煤化工展览会和发展论坛，不仅提升了公司的企业形象，也使得我公司具有完全自主知识产权的高温浆态床费托合成集成技术得到了业内人士更多的关注和认可。相信我们秉承“支撑和引导先进、规范的煤制油产业”的发展战略目标，将为煤制油事业描绘出更加灿烂美好的明天。（郝晶晶）', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '4', '1', '', '', '');
