INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9b68be0079', 'Project design and contracting', '2015-12-01 11:34:50', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>&nbsp;&nbsp;In order to speed up the industrialization process of large-scale CTL project and convert scientific and technical achievements into productive forces, Synfuels (China) Technology Co., Ltd (hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;Synfuels China&rdquo;) shall concentrate superior engineering resources to improve engineering ability of developing large-scale CTL production equipment and make efforts to solve the engineering and technological problems during the industrialization of CTL, forming a seamless industrialized supporting system of R&amp;D-technology-engineering design-EPC contracting. Therefore, Synfuels China sets up a professional engineering design and development division, i.e. Synfuels (China) Engineering Co., Ltd, and based on which, develops a series of business including the design of CTL production installation and relevant chemical process, EPC contracting, R&amp;D and design of professional equipment, contracting business of professional equipment processing, relevant energy-chemical and coal-chemical design and EPC contracting, project supervision and consulting , project construction management and other services.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;With 343 existing engineering staff and 55 project managerial staff, Synfuels (China) Engineering Co., Ltd has the ownership of a number of patents and proprietary technologies, being able to conduct core technological design and project management. As the current leader of engineering R&amp;D and design in CTL field of China, the company has received (chemical engineering) professional A-class of &quot;Engineering Design Qualification Certificate&quot; and &quot;Foreign-contracted Projects Qualification Certificate&quot; in the industries of chemical engineering, petrochemical and pharmaceuticals. The company also has other qualification certificates including C-class consulting qualification of chemical industry, pressure vessel design qualification (A-class) and pressure pipeline design qualification (GB, GC, GD category). Additionally, the company has obtained the approval certificates of engineering design, engineering consulting, project contracting (including procurement, construction management, car service) and project management.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;At present, the company has formed a set of process-package technology development and engineering design achievements covering four standardized series of 0.5 million ton / year, 1 million tons / year, 2 million tons / year and 4 million tons / year production capacity, and is undertaking a number of domestic and overseas projects covering design, engineering consulting, equipment procurement, project management, general contracting and other services. With full engagement in the all stages from the project feasibility study and evaluation reports, overall design, basic engineering design, detailed engineering design to the implementation of EPC contracting, the company can ensure the orderly convergence of all links. Now, a number of projects which includes projects of Shenhua Ningxia Coal, Shanxi Luan, Yitai Yili, Yitai Hangjin county, Yitai Ganquanbao, Beijing Energy Group and other projects have entered into a substantive engineering design and construction phase, of which three projects of Shanxi Luan, Yitai Hangjin county and Yitia Yili have assumed the EPC contracting task of core installations such as CTL device, oil processing equipment and other core devices. Additionally, the projects of Yitai Dalu and Guizhou Yufu etc are also under the project preparatory work actively. In addition to the implementation of domestic projects, we also actively explore overseas markets, for example, the 640,000 tons / year CTL project in Mongolia, the 1.2 million tons / year CTL project and 250,000 tons / year GTL project in the United States have been achieved cooperative intention with the investors, which feasibility study and design of the project have been started.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition, the engineering design team of the company actively involves in the technical amplification research, and cooperates closely with the technical personnel of the R&amp;D center of the company. With unique idea and recognition for the process of converting new technology to industrialization, the engineering design team meanwhile has the capability of second research and design development for technological process and special equipment. The technical team of the company adopts the mode of seamless connection between engineering design development and technical research process to ensure the smooth implementation of technology to industrial transformation, which will also provide high-quality technical supports and services for the industry.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383bc91100cc', '1', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d44e92803a0', '', '2015-12-01 19:19:35', '此次展览会专业性强，覆盖面广，旨在展示行业最新发展动态，前瞻市场趋势，在石化产业振兴规划实施之时，煤化工产业转型之际，聚焦行业发展热点，展示中国新型煤化工未来的广阔前景。本届展览会的参展商有内蒙古伊泰煤制油有限责任公司、上海华谊集团公司、神华集团有限责任公司、中科院大连化学物理研究所、道达尔（中国）投资有限责任公司、壳牌（中国）有限公司等国内外众多从事煤制烯烃、煤制醇醚燃料、煤制乙二醇、煤制天然气以及煤制油等现代煤化工行业的企事业单位，协同煤气化、煤焦化和煤制化肥等煤化工技术及装备提供商，展示了全球最新的煤化工技术和装备。通过本次大会搭建的展览平台，在此次展览会上，我公司样式新颖大气的展台、内容切实详尽的展板以及公司宣传片、F-T合成柴油和蜡的实物样品吸引了大批人士前来参观、咨询。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '2', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/IMG_1907.JPG', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9b6c20007b', '油品加工技术研究', '2015-12-01 11:34:51', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中科合成油技术有限公司的最大化生产柴油技术以生产</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">0<sup>#</sup>~-20<sup>#</sup></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">洁净柴油为主要目的。该技术针对煤间接液化中间产品量体设计，包含烯烃叠合、加氢精制、加氢裂化及异构降凝工艺，高效的将低碳烯烃、重质烃转化为中间油品，并将柴油中的直链烷烃转化为支链烷烃，最大程度生产柴油产品，副产低芳石脑油。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513837bb9600a4', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/waterTre2.png', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515cffdb950290', '2014年全国大学生/研究生能源化工春令营圆满结束', '2015-12-01 18:04:10', '草长莺飞，春意盎然，明媚的春光里，中科合成油技术有限公司与煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室联合举办的首届2014年全国大学生/研究生能源化工春令营开营了。本次春令营举办目的是为了让在读大学生和研究生深入了解我国现阶段能源化工技术和产业的发展现状，鼓励更多有才能和创造力的年轻人加入到该领域的技术研发和产业化团队中来。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b86a50004e', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/IMG_0459.JPG', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9c1dea007d', 'Gasoline Processing Technology', '2015-12-01 11:35:36', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>Synfuels China&rsquo;s Gasoline-maximized Technology is used for the main purpose of production of 92~98# clean gasoline. This technology, including fluid catalytic cracking, etherification, and catalytic reforming process, paired with the indirect CTL syncrude, provides a superior ability to crack heavy syncrude to gasoline, etherify tert-carbon olefin and convert short-straight-chain alkanes to aromatics. It is best suited to upgrade FTS syncrude for producing clean gasoline without sulfur.<br />\r\nThe Gasoline Technology Process selectively converts FTS heavy syncrude and light alkanes to gasoline, utilizing fluid-bed, fixed-bed, catalytic distillation and moving-bed equipments. The following are detailed steps about the gasoline process:<br />\r\nFTS heavy oil fluid catalytic cracking process based on a zeolitic catalyst to gasoline and gas products，which is rich of tert-carbon olefins<br />\r\nEtherify the tert-carbon olefin of FCC product with methanol to produce high octane number gasoline component by fixed-bed and catalytic distillation equipment<br />\r\nConvert short-straight-chain alkanes to high aromatic content gasoline component by moving-bed reactor<br />\r\nObtain the terminal clean gasoline product by blending FCC gasoline，Etherified&nbsp;asoline，and reformed gasoline components</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513839900500b6', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/frozen4.png', '');
