INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d45897903a4', '', '2015-12-01 19:20:17', '本届论坛由国家发改委、工业和信息化部、国家能源局、国资委、中国科学院、中国工程院、中国石油和化学工业协会、内蒙古伊泰集团、神华集团、兖矿集团、中科合成油技术有限公司等强势专家阵容组成，旨在站在行业高端，探讨透视煤化工能源的政策和发展动态。在此次论坛上，我公司研发中心主任杨勇博士做了题为“自主CTL技术研发及产业化应用”的专题报告。报告以中科CTL技术产业化布局为切入点，对煤制油过程分析、关键技术点和技术开发过程中的理论基础、工程基础进行了详细阐述，重点介绍了中科合成油技术有限公司独特的高温浆态床费托合成集成技术（HTSFTP）及其技术优势，以及该技术在内蒙古伊泰和山西潞安两个示范项目的应用情况，最后在对煤间接液化美好的展望中结束了本次报告。杨勇博士的报告获得了与会代表的极大关注，引发了热烈的讨论。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '3', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/IMG_1987.JPG', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9db8ed008a', 'Research on analysis and test technology', '2015-12-01 11:37:21', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>With chemical adsorption instrument, physical adsorption instrument, M&ouml;ssbauer instrument, high-resolution transmission and scanning electron microscopy, GC-MS, FTIR, and other large-scale characterizing instrument, Synfuels China can analyze the surface and bulk structure of heterogeneous catalysts, focusing on solving the scientific and technological issues with overall, critical and fundamental functions in the research on F-T synthesis catalyst structure and product details of the composition.<br />\r\nSince there are large differences of property and composition between indirect CTL and various oil from existing petroleum processing and production route, Synfuels China also conducts the research on the method of analyzing and testing products compositions and the technology of testing oil performance covering indirect CTL oil and wax as well as other products, and research on the supervision of raw material and intermediate production process as well as analysis and test of products in the process of indirect CTL Fischer-Tropsch synthesis production, which provide a reliable operation basis for quality control of synthetic oil production process, establishing and developing relevant standard analytical and testing methods.</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513837dc2800a6', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/fxcsjsy.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9e759d008c', '工艺及集成技术研究', '2015-12-01 11:38:10', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>High Temperature Slurry-bed Fischer-Tropsch Synthesis process (HTSFTSP) is a key technology of converting syngas derived from coal, natural gas or biomass into sulfur-free clean diesel, which is characterized of higher diesel yield, lower methane selectivity, higher process-thermal efficiency etc, improving &nbsp;availably the plant profitability.<br />\r\nCoal-based high temperature slurry-bed FTS technology includes three parts: syngas production (coal gasification results in syngas and its purification), Fischer-Tropsch synthesis (high Temperature slurry-bed Fischer-Tropsch synthesis and products separation), oil processing (the process of products results in clean diesel, naphtha and LPG), which has following typical features:<br />\r\nCheap iFe-based FTS catalyst has extremely high activity and stability<br />\r\nThe High Temperature Slurry-bed Bubble Column Reactor with Completely independent intellectual property rights has higher thermal efficiency<br />\r\nThe unique talented technology of product processing maximizes the production of high quality clean diesel free of sulphur and nitrogen.<br />\r\nThe optimized overall-plant process integration minimizes the investment in equipment.&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo study each technical details and optimize each key equipment based on first principles.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8514791fb015147a38a9d0016', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/gyBJ.png', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9e76ad008e', '技术许可与服务', '2015-12-01 11:38:10', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>Synfuels (China) Technology Co., Ltd (hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;Synfuels China&rdquo;&rdquo;) has independently developed CTL technologies including CTL series of catalyst technology, oil processing technology as well as its catalyst, synthetic oil technology and industrial software technology, process and product analysis and testing standards, and relevant supporting technology, which thus form the whole set of process integration technology covering low-temperature slurry-bed heavy distillate oil process and high-temperature light distillate process, systematically developing the overall process simulation software and basic engineering process database from coal to the refined oil products. Based on different users, Synfuels China can carry out coal analysis, pre-planning, analysis of technical economy and product solutions as well as feasibility studies for the whole technological process including a variety of synthetic oil installation size, different coals, different types of gasifier, different types of synthetic catalysts, flexible oil processing technology and so on, meanwhile design and prepare basic material of engineering design and its technical documents including technological process package of different size of CTL project etc for users, which are used effectively to guide the industrialization of the technology. For the time being, the company has applied for 137 patented technologies and achieved ownership of 29 international patents authorization, 91 invention patents in China, developed 3 national standards of CTL technology and published more than 510 articles. Additionally, the company has the copyright of a CTL technology design software.<br />\r\nSynfuels China has a number of highly-qualified technical staff, engineering R&amp;D personnel and design engineers with many years of extensive research and development experiences, which can provide on-site technical support and technical advisory services in the phases of installation design and construction, pilot operation of installation feeding.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is the technical personnel and production operators of the plant who need training, which is the important guarantee for smooth and successful trial production and stable operation of the production installations. At the time of transformation of CTL technical achievements, Sysfuels China can supply training including theory, safety and practical operation skills in pilot plant and laboratory for the technical personnel and production operators of users, for the purpose of improving the theory level and operational skills of aforesaid personnel, ensuring safe, stable and highly efficient operation of CTL production installations.<span lang=\"EN-US\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383be53b00ce', '1', '1', '', '', '');
