INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515b9f63540092', 'Fine chemical engineering technology research', '2015-12-01 11:39:11', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>The fine chemical engineering research fields of SYNFUELS mainly include basic research and industrial development in catalyst hydration of fine chemicals, dehydration and coupling reaction. Maleic anhydride, furfuraldehyde and others are the main platform compounds producing fine chemical engineering products such asGBL, THF, 2-MF and 2-MTHF after catalyst hydration.Besides, there is technology research on producing ethylene glycol catalysts by catalytic hydration of dimethyl oxalate and development of new copper based catalysts of better activity, selectivity and life. Among these, the R&amp;D work in coupling technology of producing GBL and 2-MF has won the Second Prize of National Technological Invention.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383823d700aa', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/jxh1.png', '');
