INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081519e6dd20151a88b9eae003e', 'The furfuraldehyde hydrogenation technology', '2015-12-16 10:08:21', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>Furfuraldehyde is an important derivative of furan ring. It has active chemical properties, which can produce many derivatives through oxidization, condensation and many other reactions. It is widely used in compound plastic, pharmacy, pesticide and other industries. SYNFUELS uses hydrogenation technology to selective change furfuraldehyde into 2 - methyl furan, 2 - methyl tetrahydrofuran and other chemicals. For example, it mainly produces 2 - methyl furan on Cu-based catalysts. It mainly produces furan and tetrahydrofuran on precious-metal-based catalysts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" mso-bidi-language:=\"\" mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\"><!--[endif]--></span></body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383ac0ce00c2', '1', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d3447f2034c', '北京市科委主任闫傲霜一行考察调研我公司', '2015-12-01 19:01:26', '9月7日，北京市科委主任闫傲霜一行到我公司怀柔总部基地考察调研，怀柔区副区长吴群刚、怀柔区科委主要领导及我公司执行总裁郑大为陪同调研。\r\n \r\n闫傲霜一行此次到怀柔主要是考察调研怀柔区科技工作开展情况和中科院科教产业园区的建设进展情况。而中科合成油技术有限公司作为怀柔区重点引进扶植的高新技术企业和怀柔区政府提出的“一站两园三项目”的关键组成部分，受到了北京市科委和怀柔区政府的高度重视。\r\n \r\n调研期间，科委领导一行首先观看了公司的主题宣传片。随后，郑总向大家详细阐述了公司的机构人员设置、技术开发进展、业务开展情况和“十二五”期间发展计划和前景，希望北京市科委和怀柔区政府能够一如既往地关心和支持公司各项事业的发展。在听取介绍之后，闫傲霜主任表示，科委将为公司的发展提供良好的外部环境，并将全力支持公司高新技术企业的申报工作。\r\n \r\n最后，科委领导一行实地参观了公司怀柔总部研发大楼。（综合部 程岩）', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b8c3470052', '1', '1', '', '', '2010-9-7');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba1f763009c', '伊泰煤基合成油示范项目(meyou!)', '2015-12-01 11:42:00', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>The main construction unit for1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project is Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd., which was built on October 29, 2009. Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. is a joint-stock enterprise founded by the Chinese Top-500 Enterprise and the nation&rsquo;s top coal enterprises- Inner Mongolia Yitai Group Co., Ltd. and Inner Mongolia Yitai Coal Co., Ltd. Yitai group is a large enterprise mainly engaged in coal production and extended in the railway transportation, coal chemical industry, belonging to the Chinese Top-500 Enterprise, the National Top-100 Coal Enterprise and the Inner Mongolia Top-50 Coal Enterprise. Yitai Coal Co., Ltd. the first B+H listing enterprise in coal industry. Trademark of &ldquo;Yitai&rdquo; is the first &ldquo;Chinese Well-known Trademark&rdquo; in the coal industry.<br />\r\nTotal investment of 1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. RMB 19 billion, and the projected is located in South Project Zone of Hangjinqi Dugui Tala Industrial Park in Erdos City. The project was formally put on record by the Development and Reform Commission of Inner Mongolia in October 2012, and has been included in the &ldquo;Planning of Coal Deep Processing Demonstration Project of Twelfth Five Year of Inner Mongolia Autonomous Region&rdquo;.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '0', '', '402881e8513780600151383dd1fe00d9', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/ytmj_1.jpg', '');
