INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d34f6fc0351', 'The imethyl oxalate hydrogenation', '2015-12-01 19:02:10', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">The imethyl oxalate catalyst hydrogenation producing glycol is a key process in &ldquo;coal to glycol&rdquo;. SYNFUELS solve the low activity and short life problems of current imethyl oxalate hydrogenation catalyst by developing the new generation of high-performance imethyl oxalate hydrogenation copper-based catalyst. Production efficiency of glycol can reach 0.15-0.3g/g-cat/h. The collection rate of glycol is higher than 95%. It is steadier, renewable and total life exceeds 2 years. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">Technical development milestones:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">2007-2011 Basic research on the fixed-bed catalyst tests of dimethyl oxalate ester hydrogenation</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">2012-2013 Integrated optimization on the fixed-bed catalyst tests of dimethyl oxalate ester hydrogenation</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">2014-2015 Scale-up technology on preparing fixed-bed catalyst tests of dimethyl oxalate ester hydrogenation</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">Catalysts of outstanding nature have been designed and prepared after research on hydration, dehydration and coupling reactions, using the hydrogen spillover theory. Series of chemicals have been produced and about 150 tons of catalysts have been provided.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; text-indent: 1.8pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">About 15 granted patents have been made in the aspect of fine chemical engineering research; Over 50 professional papers have been published in English; About 20 doctors and masters have been developed; The second prize of National Technological Invention has been won once; The first prize in technological inventionof the Petrochemical Association has been won once; The second prize of Shanxi Provincial Technology has been won twice.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151383af0f400c4', '1', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba2b91400a0', 'Stepwise liquefaction technology', '2015-12-01 11:42:49', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt;line-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">The stepwise liquefaction technology originally proposed by Synfuels China, integrates the low temperature pyrolysis technology, modern gasification technology, and advanced slurry bed FTS synthetic technology of coal, heavy oil and biomass etc. With the stepwise liquefaction technology, the overall energy efficiency of CTL could be improved from 38%-43% to 50-55%. A pilot plant of 1t/d scale has been constructed in 2010</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">and several pilot tests have been completed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-top:6.0pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;margin-bottom:6.0pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-para-margin-bottom:.5gd;text-indent:26.9pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\nmso-outline-level:1;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">During the liquefaction, the coal (heavy oil or biomass) shall be first partly hydrogenated at moderate condition, which results in some light oil; The semi-coke residue after hydrogenation is gasified and converted to syngas. The Syngas is converted to liquid fuel by Fischer-Tropsch synthesis. Different levels of heat released from gasification and Fischer-Tropsch synthesis is used for the preheating and dehydration of coal, heavy oil, biomass and other raw material. The liquid fuel from FTS process is blended with light oil from partly hydrogenation process to produce diesel and gasoline.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015138384d8500ac', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/yhjsyj.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d37c2e5035e', '', '2015-12-01 19:05:14', '煤基多联产项目工艺方案论证会在京召开\r\n \r\n2011年9月3日山西潞安集团资源综合利用一期180万吨/年煤基多联产项目工艺方案论证会在北京西苑饭店隆重召开。中科合成油技术有限公司总经理李永旺、总工程师曹立仁、工程部部长董根全,中科合成油工程有限公司总经理唐益民、总工程师余晓忠、副总经理张立等参加了会议。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b8c3470052', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/la1.JPG', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba2c25800a2', '', '2015-12-01 11:42:51', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the provider of core technology, Synfuels China Technology Co., Ltd. provides technology licensing and package of oil synthesis and oil processing. As the first General Institute, Synfuels China undertakes the general technical scheme design, overall design and technical checking of whole plant of 1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. as well as oil synthesis device, oil processing device, detailed foundation engineering design of liquid material storage system and EPC general contracting.<br />\r\nSynfuels China finished the overall design of 1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. in June 2013; preparation of project technical process in September 2013; and the delivery of basic design finished project in June 2014; Synfuels China launched detailed foundation engineering design of liquid material storage system in April 2014; EPC contracting work fully started in July 2014；It is expected that detailed design will be finished in April 2015, the main equipment installation will be in place in August 2015 and the mechanical completion will be realized at the end of May 2016.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '0', '', '402881e8513780600151383dd1fe00d9', '2', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/ytmj_2.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba388a700a4', '技术研发历程', '2015-12-01 11:43:42', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>2002-2008 &nbsp;R&amp;D of stepwise liquefaction technology on laboratory scale<br />\r\n2008-2009 &nbsp;Construction of the stepwise liquefaction pilot plant<br />\r\n2010-2014 &nbsp;Pilot test for the partly hydrogenation of brown coal, soft coal, coal tar, and heavy oil</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85138e859015138fe8fea0004', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/mqhjs_3.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba41a1300a6', 'Advantage：', '2015-12-01 11:44:19', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>The overall energy efficiency could be increased from 38-43% of indirect liquefactiontechnology to 50-55%<br />\r\nThe reaction condition of partly hydrogenation is milder than that of the direct liquefaction technology，which is easy to be realized and operated stably.<br />\r\nThe oil product produced from stepwise liquefaction technology is easy to be refined and blended, and is suitable for the production of high quality gasoline and diesel&nbsp;</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85138e859015138fedcf40006', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/mqhjs_4.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba49d8e00a8', '神华示范项目', '2015-12-01 11:44:53', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua Group Co., Ltd., one of the key enterprises directly under the state-owned assets supervision and administration of state-owned, is an integrated energy company with the main business of coal production, transportation, power generation, coal and coal chemical industry. The coal-to-liquid (CTL) and coal-to-chemicals, the strategic energy projects of Shenhua Group, will become one of the most important pillar industries of Shenhua Group.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua coal liquefaction project which was built in Ordos, Inner Mongolia, is unique in the world. National Development and Reform Commission approved the process optimization of Shenhua coal liquefaction project, and its first phase in August, 2004. The first phase, with 3.2 million tons per year, is made up of three production lines. To minimize and avoid the risk which industrialization may encounter for the first time, the first phase would proceed step by step: to build a production line of 1.08 million tons/year, which was also known as the first project and then to construct the two remaining production lines.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua Group planned an indirect liquefaction project while implementing direct coal liquefaction project, and it made contact with the party who had technology. But the negotiation progressed slowly due to harsh conditions which were asked by the party. On August 29, 2005, Shenhua Group determined to adopt the coal-based liquid fuel industrialization technology (synthesis technology), which was developed by synthetic oil engineering research center </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">CAS Shanxi Coal Chemical Research Institute</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">(</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Synfuels China Technology Co., Ltd.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">) after long-time after investigation and comparison. The technology would be the core of the demonstration project. Therefore, the coal indirect liquefaction demonstration project of Shenhua Group had a scale of 0.16 million tons/year (the project for Shenhua 829).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513842650f00db', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/shsf_1.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d4ccf4c03c8', '', '2015-12-01 19:28:13', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">On June 6, 2007, FGBNY [2007] No.1302 &ldquo;About Increasing Synthetic Oil Device in the First Phase of the Shenhua Coal Direct Liquefaction from General Office of the NDRC&rdquo; agreed that Shenhua Group can rely on direct liquefaction project utility system and auxiliary facilities. In the first phase, Shenhua would increase a set of 180,000 tons/year of synthetic oil device, with synthesis integration technology.&nbsp;</span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua coal indirect liquefaction demonstration project was launched on August 29, 2005. Shenhua 829 demonstration project was divided into two regions (zone A and zone B) due to combination process, lying in the two streets. Zone A , composed of&nbsp; fischer, refined wax filter, catalyst pretreatment and PSA area, was in the north. It was more than 35 meters away from water treatment station, computer, the third cycle water yards, phenol recovery unit to its east, zone B to its south, self-power station to its west. Zone B, with oil processing, the synthesis of water treatment, decarburization and tundish, was in the south street. It was more than 35 meters away from zone A to its north, 25 meters away from salt water processing system to its west. Zone A covered an area of 12,627 square meters, and zone B covered an area of 16,700 square meters, 6,000 square meters was for new roads, which was adding up to 35,327 square meters. So the total construction area was 9,752.6 square meters.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua group has built a perfect project management system and construction management team in constructing coal direct liquefaction project, and the operation personnel were in place. The condition was good when adding new production lines in the project management and production management. As supporters and practitioners of alternative energy development strategy, Shenhua would, as always, committed to the healthy development of the coal and coal chemical industry, advancing clean coal utilization technology progress and innovation, to provide reliable coal oil and chemical products, to ensure the safety of national energy as own duty, insisting on the quality and benefit unified, speeding up the construction of demonstration projects and industrialization development.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513842650f00db', '3', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba4aec700aa', 'Research on coal gasification research', '2015-12-01 11:44:58', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>The coal gasification technology researched and developed by SYNFUELS has provided a gasification furnace with gasification of carbon-contained solid material. During this process, carbon-contained slid material shall be gasified partially and produce crude syngas under the effects of oxygen and water steam in certain temperature and pressure. Then high H2/CO shall be produced after converting and purifying, which is suitable for coal chemical fields such as Fischer-tropsch synthesis and methanol synthesis.<br />\r\nThe gasification process is: carbon-contained solid powders are transmitted by solid pumps into somewhere near the burner of gasification furnace. They are mixed with water and oxygen and produce crudesyngas after reaction in the gasification furnace under certain temperature and pressure. After gasification, ashes in the coal became furnace slag in gravity and flow downward to the slag sink under the gasification furnace. The generated high-temperature coal gas takes the melting ash residue into the rapid cooling zone of high and low temperature in the upper part of gasification furnace. The melting ash among the high-temperature coal gas is condensed into solid powders. Some fall down to the gasification zone below. Some flow with syngas further into the outlet of gasification furnace above. The crude syngas after two rounds of rapid cooling then enters the later processing unit. The main features of the technology: the processing amount is 4000t/d. Dry powders are fed in by solid pumps. There are water cooling walls, side-wall burner and internal rapid cooing inside the furnace.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513838767e00ae', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/mqhjsyj.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba4f24400ac', '', '2015-12-01 11:45:15', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua 829 is located in Ordos City, Inner Mongolia autonomous region in Yijin Huoluo Banner, in the northwest of Shenhua coal direct liquefaction plants now. The address is the Inner Mongolia autonomous region (referred to as Yi Banner) in Yijin Huoluo Banner, about 35 km away from the flag town, 80 km from DongSheng to its north, 200 km from Baotou City.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">Shenhua coal indirect liquefaction synthetic oil device is equivalent to 829 project in the gasification device with a lateral line, and the syngas is the raw material of the project. According to the special requirements of indirect liquefaction technology, relying on coal, the device directly liquefied to the existing utilities, auxiliary facilities and reserved space. Compared with the complete indirect liquefaction of coal production line, the device got rid of the air separation, gas generation, and the utility of capital construction investment. The total investment is about a half of the investment to the coal liquefaction production lines, at the same time, it can greatly shorten the construction period.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:27.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n仿宋\">The project took 7,920 hours to finish the scale of 18 tons/year synthetic oil, which included liquid gas 49,600 tons/year, 35,700 tons/year naphtha, diesel oil, 98,100 tons/year. Indirect liquefaction production of diesel oil was in high quality, and its number was more than 70. This kind of diesel can be used as blending base oil. People can put the direct liquefaction into base oil in order to produce the new diesel, with the production of 189300 tons per year, which met the new country </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ⅲ</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">standard. Other direct liquefaction diesel, after adding cetane , would leave factory, according to Europe </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ⅱ</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:仿宋\">standard. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513842650f00db', '2', '1', '', '', '');
