INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d4bfd3d03c4', '公司管理体系建设动员暨培训工作会议召开', '2015-12-01 19:27:19', '公司管理体系建设动员暨培训工作会议于3月29日至30日在北京召开。执行总裁郑大为出席会议并做动员讲话，公司各子公司、分公司、各部门相关负责人、技术骨干及咨询单位代表参加了会议。\r\n \r\n郑总在动员讲话中结合公司总体发展目标和管理现状，指出全面提升管理水平是公司发展的必然要求，管理体系建设对于公司做好科研和生产工作具有十分重要的意义，同时也将为公司今后上市打下扎实的基础。郑总在会上强调，建立质量管理体系是公司长期健康发展的要求和保证，也是公司今年的重点工作之一，各子公司、分公司、各部门要高度重视，积极配合，选派得力人员，结合公司实际情况开展工作, 要重内容、轻形式，讲实用，求成效，确保按期圆满完成质量管理体系建立及运行工作，为公司今后的发展奠定坚实的基础。\r\n \r\n动员会后，咨询单位老师结合前期调研情况，为参会人员做了质量管理体系基础知识和PDCA过程应用方法培训，并组织了现场测试和讲解，圆满完成了预定培训目标。（技术质量部 罗芬）', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '1', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d4ca9d603c6', '公司召开2009年年终表彰暨新春联谊会', '2015-12-01 19:28:04', '江山秀丽春增色，事业辉煌虎更威。2010年1月21日，中科合成油技术有限公司在太谷梅苑山庄召开了2009年年终表彰暨新春联谊会，公司郑大为总裁、赵璐琦副总经理、李文军财务总监、杨勇主任与技术公司全体员工一起，共联欢，同快乐！\r\n \r\n        表彰会上，郑大为总裁首先代表公司向全体员工拜了早年，祝福大家在新的一年中，新年新气象，奋发进步，事业有成！之后，郑总发表了热情洋溢的讲话，指出2009年是公司发展里程碑式的一年，在过去的一年中公司成绩满满，硕果累累，实现了合成油事业的跨越式大发展。全体员工励精图治、团结拼搏、勤奋工作、迎难而上，铸就了内蒙古伊泰集团、山西潞安集团两个年产16万吨煤制油示范厂的成功运行投产，这一切成绩的取得都是全体员工辛勤努力工作的结果，在此特别要感谢那些常年默默奉献在一线同志们，并对在2009年工作中做出突出贡献先进工作者表示祝贺。他还谈到，2010年将是中科合成油事业蓬勃向上，加速发展的一年，他相信在公司的统筹部署下，全体员工同心同德，艰苦奋斗，开拓创新，一定会谱写出合成油更加辉煌绚丽的新篇章。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/IMG_1354.JPG', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba5dd4a00ae', '内蒙古伊泰化工有限责任公司120万吨/年精细化学品示范项目', '2015-12-01 11:46:15', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>The main construction unit for1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project is Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd., which was built on October 29, 2009. Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. is a joint-stock enterprise founded by the Chinese Top-500 Enterprise and the nation&rsquo;s top coal enterprises- Inner Mongolia Yitai Group Co., Ltd. and Inner Mongolia Yitai Coal Co., Ltd. Yitai group is a large enterprise mainly engaged in coal production and extended in the railway transportation, coal chemical industry, belonging to the Chinese Top-500 Enterprise, the National Top-100 Coal Enterprise and the Inner Mongolia Top-50 Coal Enterprise. Yitai Coal Co., Ltd. the first B+H listing enterprise in coal industry. Trademark of &ldquo;Yitai&rdquo; is the first &ldquo;Chinese Well-known Trademark&rdquo; in the coal industry.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\nTotal investment of 1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. RMB 19 billion, and the projected is located in South Project Zone of Hangjinqi Dugui Tala Industrial Park in Erdos City. The project was formally put on record by the Development and Reform Commission of Inner Mongolia in October 2012, and has been included in the &ldquo;Planning of Coal Deep Processing Demonstration Project of Twelfth Five Year of Inner Mongolia Autonomous Region&rdquo;.</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513842bc0b00dd', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/jshx_1.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba62b4300b0', '', '2015-12-01 11:46:35', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>As the&nbsp;provider&nbsp;of core technology, Synfuels China Technology Co., Ltd. provides technology licensing and package of oil synthesis and oil processing. As the first General Institute, Synfuels China undertakes the general technical scheme design, overall design and technical checking of whole plant of 1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. as well as oil synthesis device, oil processing device, detailed foundation engineering design of liquid material storage system and EPC general contracting.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\nSynfuels China finished the overall design of 1.2 Million Tons/year Fine Chemicals Demonstration Project of Inner Mongolia Yitai Chemical Co., Ltd. in June 2013; preparation of project technical process in September 2013; and the delivery of basic design finished project in June 2014; Synfuels China launched detailed foundation engineering design of liquid material storage system in April 2014; EPC contracting work fully started in July 2014；It is expected that detailed design will be finished in April 2015, the main equipment installation will be in place in August 2015 and the mechanical completion will be realized at the end of May 2016.</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513842bc0b00dd', '2', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d4f289103d8', '', '2015-12-01 19:30:47', ' 报告结束后，潘锋副局长首先祝贺煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室第一届理事会成立，并对李永旺研究员长期带领科学家们奋战在工作岗位的敬业精神表示钦佩，他同时提出四点意见及建议。第一：要特别处理好上游国家重点实验室，中游国家工程实验室及下游企业技术产业化应用之间的关系，以充分发挥三个平台在各方面的优势和作用。第二：尽快组织召开第一届技术委员会会议，充分发挥各委员在其相关领域的作用，并定期召开技术委员会向国家工程实验室提供好的意见及建议。第三：国家工程实验室3年的发展建设期要遵循发改委的相关规定，在建设期间资金的使用要严按按照预算制度执行，做好档案资料的整理等各项工作，同时要做好相关管理工作，以达到验收要求的标准。第四：积极肯定煤间接液化技术对地方产业起到的重要作用，鼓励中科合成油技术有限公司继续推进该技术的发展及优化，以体现其在国家能源战略方面的作用。\r\n \r\n        接下来，刘桂菊副局长为煤间接液化技术现在的发展感到由衷的高兴、自豪，也感谢发改委支持成立国家煤间接液化工程实验室，相信实验室整个团队会逐步做好、做强！同时她指出工程实验室的下一步发展定位非常重要，要做好相关技术的前瞻和部署工作，推进工程实验室不断向前发展，同时要借助各方面的力量加快推动具有完全自主知识产权煤间接液化技术的产业化进程，她表示中科院高技术研究与发展局将不遗余力的配合实验室的各项工作。[PAGE]\r\n \r\n        最后，袁军处长总结性发言，指出了未来国家工程实验室的发展方向及评价标准，他指出现在全国国家工程实验室已发展到80多家，由于各个承办单位不一，在以知识创新为重点内容的“十二五”期间，如何在管理及布置上抓紧各实验室的建设及规划成为当前最重要的内容。今后，发改委将制定一系列指标及评价标准，用于衡量国家工程实验室与生产实际相结合的情况及能力。\r\n \r\n        煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室（英文名称：National Engineering Laboratory for Indirect Coal Liquefaction）是由国家发展和改革委员会2008年7月批复建设的产学研相结合的研究开发机构。该实验室依托在中科院山西煤化所，其它理事单位有：中科合成油技术有限公司，中国石油和化学工业协会，中国科学院高技术研究与发展局，中国科学院计划财务局，内蒙古伊泰集团有限公司、山西潞安矿业集团有限公司、徐州矿务集团有限公司、锦西化工机械（集团）有限责任公司。\r\n \r\n        工程实验室的建设目标和任务是：站在国家煤炭间接液化产业发展和能源战略的高度，开展具有自主创新能力的煤炭间接费托合成技术及其匹配技术与工程化的工程研发，确保自主技术的先进性和可持续发展，并使其成为煤合成油产业的催化剂和工艺包的供应商及技术支撑和服务者，为煤炭间接液化研究和产业的健康有序发展提供长期稳定的技术支撑，使工程实验室成为我国一流的煤炭间接液化技术研发基地、产业化技术支撑基地和高水平人才培养基地。项目建设期为3年。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '3', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d14003802e1', '内蒙古国际清洁煤化工博览会暨内蒙古煤化工发展论坛在包头召开', '2015-12-01 18:26:10', '2013年10月26日首届中国•内蒙古（包头）国际清洁煤化工博览会暨内蒙古煤化工发展论坛，在包头国际会展中心开幕，中科合成油技术有限公司受邀参加了此次论坛和展览。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b84c3c004c', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/gj1.JPG', '2013-10-26');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba7355c00b4', '山西潞安矿业（集团）有限责任公司高硫煤清洁利用油化电热一体化示范项目', '2015-12-01 11:47:43', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">High-sulfur&nbsp;Coal&nbsp;and&nbsp;Oil-electric&nbsp;Integration&nbsp;Demonstration&nbsp;Project&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Coal-based&nbsp;Clean&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.(call&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Integration&nbsp;Demonstration&nbsp;Project&nbsp;for&nbsp;short)&nbsp;is&nbsp;invested&nbsp;by&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Coal-based&nbsp;Clean&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.(a&nbsp;subsidiary&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Mining&nbsp;Group)&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;total&nbsp;investment&nbsp;is&nbsp;RMB&nbsp;21.3&nbsp;billion.&nbsp;As&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;seven&nbsp;large&nbsp;coal&nbsp;enterprises&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Province,&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Mining&nbsp;Group&nbsp;is&nbsp;coal&nbsp;based&nbsp;and&nbsp;pluralistic&nbsp;developed,&nbsp;ranking&nbsp;372&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;World&nbsp;Top-500&nbsp;in&nbsp;2014.&nbsp;As&nbsp;a&nbsp;wholly&nbsp;owned&nbsp;subsidiary&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Mining&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Coal-based&nbsp;Clean&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;is&nbsp;fully&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;implementation&nbsp;and&nbsp;normal&nbsp;operation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Integration&nbsp;Demonstration&nbsp;Project.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Facing&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;slump&nbsp;coal&nbsp;market,&nbsp;implementation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Integration&nbsp;Demonstration&nbsp;Project&nbsp;exerts&nbsp;significant&nbsp;influence&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;transformation&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal&nbsp;industry&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Province.&nbsp;As&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;comprehensive&nbsp;transformation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Benchmarking&nbsp;Projects,&nbsp;it&nbsp;also&nbsp;plays&nbsp;an&nbsp;important&nbsp;role&nbsp;in&nbsp;actively&nbsp;implementing&nbsp;the&nbsp;adjustment&nbsp;of&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;structure&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;country&nbsp;and&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Province,&nbsp;changing&nbsp;the&nbsp;mode&nbsp;of&nbsp;economic&nbsp;growth,&nbsp;realizing&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;diversified&nbsp;energy&nbsp;structure,&nbsp;promoting&nbsp;the&nbsp;implementation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;national&nbsp;energy&nbsp;strategy,&nbsp;accelerating&nbsp;the&nbsp;transformation&nbsp;from&nbsp;coal&nbsp;to&nbsp;coal&nbsp;chemical&nbsp;industry&nbsp;for&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Province&nbsp;and&nbsp;speeding&nbsp;up&nbsp;construction&nbsp;of&nbsp;new&nbsp;energy&nbsp;and&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;base.<br />\r\nLocated&nbsp;in&nbsp;Wangqiao&nbsp;Industrial&nbsp;Park&nbsp;in&nbsp;Xiangyuan&nbsp;County&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Province&nbsp;and&nbsp;relied&nbsp;on&nbsp;coal-based&nbsp;liquid&nbsp;fuel&nbsp;slurry&nbsp;bed&nbsp;technology&nbsp;developed&nbsp;by&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;with&nbsp;independent&nbsp;IPR,&nbsp;Shanxi&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Coal-based&nbsp;Clean&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;uses&nbsp;crude&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;gas&nbsp;from&nbsp;coal&nbsp;pressurized&nbsp;gasification&nbsp;after&nbsp;the&nbsp;removal&nbsp;of&nbsp;acid&nbsp;gases,&nbsp;through&nbsp;the&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;process,&nbsp;high&nbsp;temperature&nbsp;slurry&nbsp;bed&nbsp;hydrotreating&nbsp;and&nbsp;FCC&nbsp;process&nbsp;to&nbsp;transform&nbsp;into&nbsp;a&nbsp;direct&nbsp;export&nbsp;or&nbsp;for&nbsp;deep&nbsp;processing&nbsp;of&nbsp;finished&nbsp;oil;&nbsp;the&nbsp;plant&nbsp;includes&nbsp;air&nbsp;separation&nbsp;device,&nbsp;coal&nbsp;gasification&nbsp;device,&nbsp;cleaning&nbsp;device,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;device,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device,&nbsp;intermediate&nbsp;tank&nbsp;farm,&nbsp;tail&nbsp;gas&nbsp;to&nbsp;hydrogen&nbsp;production&nbsp;device,&nbsp;thermoelectric&nbsp;device,&nbsp;the&nbsp;whole&nbsp;plant&nbsp;water&nbsp;system,&nbsp;steam&nbsp;system,&nbsp;fire&nbsp;protection&nbsp;system,&nbsp;power&nbsp;supply&nbsp;and&nbsp;distribution&nbsp;system,&nbsp;the&nbsp;liquid&nbsp;material&nbsp;storage&nbsp;and&nbsp;transportation&nbsp;facilities,&nbsp;solid&nbsp;material&nbsp;storage&nbsp;facilities,&nbsp;center&nbsp;laboratory,&nbsp;central&nbsp;control&nbsp;room&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;front&nbsp;zone&nbsp;of&nbsp;plant&nbsp;facilities&nbsp;etc.</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151384398ae00e0', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/layt_1.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba8374600b6', '', '2015-12-01 11:48:49', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">The&nbsp;project&nbsp;construction&nbsp;scale&nbsp;is&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;annual&nbsp;production&nbsp;capacity&nbsp;of&nbsp;1.05&nbsp;million&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal&nbsp;based&nbsp;synthetic&nbsp;oil,&nbsp;of&nbsp;which&nbsp;LPG&nbsp;is&nbsp;90,000&nbsp;tons,&nbsp;naphtha&nbsp;is&nbsp;250,000&nbsp;tons&nbsp;and&nbsp;diesel&nbsp;is&nbsp;710,000&nbsp;tons;&nbsp;the&nbsp;sixteen&nbsp;Cetane&nbsp;value&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;quality&nbsp;diesel&nbsp;reaches&nbsp;74.8,&nbsp;and&nbsp;exhaust&nbsp;emissions&nbsp;meets&nbsp;the&nbsp;Euro&nbsp;V&nbsp;standard.<br />\r\nThe&nbsp;project&nbsp;obtained&nbsp;the&nbsp;permit&nbsp;issued&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;NDRC&nbsp;in&nbsp;July&nbsp;2012&nbsp;and&nbsp;completed&nbsp;the&nbsp;overall&nbsp;design&nbsp;in&nbsp;December&nbsp;2012.&nbsp;Currently,&nbsp;the&nbsp;project&nbsp;has&nbsp;entered&nbsp;a&nbsp;substantive&nbsp;construction&nbsp;phase.&nbsp;According&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;identified&nbsp;goals&nbsp;of&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;linkage&nbsp;test&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;finished&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;2015,&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;project&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;ready&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;commissioned.<br />\r\nSynfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;assumed&nbsp;a&nbsp;total&nbsp;design&nbsp;work&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;project,&nbsp;including&nbsp;technical&nbsp;package&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;and&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;device,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device,&nbsp;intermediate&nbsp;tank&nbsp;farm,&nbsp;cleaning&nbsp;device,&nbsp;whole&nbsp;technical&nbsp;process&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;outer&nbsp;heating&nbsp;tube,&nbsp;power&nbsp;supply&nbsp;and&nbsp;distribution&nbsp;system&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;central&nbsp;control&nbsp;room&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;EPC&nbsp;general&nbsp;contracting&nbsp;task&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;device,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device&nbsp;and&nbsp;intermediate&nbsp;tank&nbsp;farm.&nbsp;In&nbsp;May&nbsp;2013,&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;completed&nbsp;the&nbsp;package&nbsp;design&nbsp;process&nbsp;for&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;and&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device;&nbsp;in&nbsp;August&nbsp;2013,&nbsp;it&nbsp;completed&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;foundation&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;and&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device;&nbsp;in&nbsp;October&nbsp;2014,&nbsp;it&nbsp;completed&nbsp;detailed&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;and&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;device;&nbsp;Currently,&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;under&nbsp;construction&nbsp;and&nbsp;implementation&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;interim&nbsp;handover&nbsp;will&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;August&nbsp;2015.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151384398ae00e0', '2', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/layt_2.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba8fe4600b8', '4 Million Coal Indirect Liquefaction Demonstration Project of Shenhua Ningxia Coal Group', '2015-12-01 11:49:40', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Shenhua&nbsp;Ningxia&nbsp;Coal&nbsp;Group&nbsp;4&nbsp;million&nbsp;coal&nbsp;indirect&nbsp;liquefaction&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;project&nbsp;is&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;basic&nbsp;structure&nbsp;of&nbsp;China&#39;s&nbsp;primary&nbsp;energy,&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;&quot;lack&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil,&nbsp;less&nbsp;gas,&nbsp;rich&nbsp;in&nbsp;coal&quot;.&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;established&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;national&nbsp;coal&nbsp;deep&nbsp;processing&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;project,&nbsp;which&nbsp;aims&nbsp;to&nbsp;meet&nbsp;the&nbsp;rapid&nbsp;growth&nbsp;of&nbsp;China&#39;s&nbsp;oil&nbsp;consumption&nbsp;demand,&nbsp;safeguard&nbsp;our&nbsp;energy&nbsp;security&nbsp;and&nbsp;promote&nbsp;national&nbsp;long-term&nbsp;energy&nbsp;development&nbsp;strategy.&nbsp;The&nbsp;project&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&#39;s&nbsp;largest&nbsp;single&nbsp;set&nbsp;of&nbsp;devices&nbsp;coal&nbsp;liquefaction&nbsp;project&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;also&nbsp;the&nbsp;No.1&nbsp;project&nbsp;to&nbsp;spur&nbsp;economic&nbsp;and&nbsp;social&nbsp;development&nbsp;by&nbsp;leaps&nbsp;and&nbsp;bounds&nbsp;of&nbsp;Ningxia&nbsp;Hui&nbsp;Autonomous&nbsp;Region.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">The&nbsp;NDRC&nbsp;issued&nbsp;&ldquo;Notice&nbsp;of&nbsp;Regulating&nbsp;the&nbsp;Orderly&nbsp;Development&nbsp;of&nbsp;Coal&nbsp;Chemical&nbsp;Industry&rdquo;&nbsp;in&nbsp;March&nbsp;2011,&nbsp;which&nbsp;clearly&nbsp;required&nbsp;great&nbsp;efforts&nbsp;on&nbsp;coal&nbsp;processing&nbsp;pilot.&nbsp;After&nbsp;the&nbsp;issue&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Notice,&nbsp;ingxia&nbsp;Autonomous&nbsp;Region,&nbsp;Shenhua&nbsp;Ningxia&nbsp;Coal&nbsp;Group&nbsp;and&nbsp;Advisory&nbsp;Company&nbsp;had&nbsp;re-studied&nbsp;the&nbsp;construction&nbsp;program&nbsp;in&nbsp;accordance&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;requirements&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;project.&nbsp;The&nbsp;NDRC&nbsp;held&nbsp;a&nbsp;symposium&nbsp;with&nbsp;experts,&nbsp;and&nbsp;they&nbsp;gradually&nbsp;formed&nbsp;a&nbsp;consensus&nbsp;in&nbsp;all&nbsp;aspects.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">After&nbsp;evaluation&nbsp;of&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;test&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;validation,&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;self-developed&nbsp;technology&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;number&nbsp;of&nbsp;technical&nbsp;and&nbsp;economic&nbsp;indicators&nbsp;is&nbsp;in&nbsp;an&nbsp;advanced&nbsp;level&nbsp;all&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world,&nbsp;and&nbsp;with&nbsp;ability&nbsp;to&nbsp;build&nbsp;large-scale&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;projects.&nbsp;Thus,&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">decided&nbsp;to&nbsp;build&nbsp;4million&nbsp;tons/year&nbsp;coal&nbsp;indirect&nbsp;liquefaction&nbsp;project&nbsp;by&nbsp;using&nbsp;high&nbsp;temperature&nbsp;slurry&nbsp;Fischer&nbsp;Tropsch&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;technology&nbsp;of&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;with&nbsp;independent&nbsp;IPR.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">The&nbsp;project&nbsp;is&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;Ningxia&nbsp;Ning&nbsp;Dong&nbsp;Energy&nbsp;and&nbsp;Chemical&nbsp;Base&nbsp;Coal&nbsp;Chemical&nbsp;Industry&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Zone&nbsp;A,&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;total&nbsp;area&nbsp;of&nbsp;815.23&nbsp;hectares.&nbsp;The&nbsp;project&nbsp;uses&nbsp;coal&nbsp;as&nbsp;raw&nbsp;material,&nbsp;with&nbsp;an&nbsp;annual&nbsp;conversion&nbsp;of&nbsp;20.36&nbsp;million&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal,&nbsp;and&nbsp;an&nbsp;annual&nbsp;4.052&nbsp;million&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis,&nbsp;including&nbsp;2.733&nbsp;million&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;diesel&nbsp;reconcile,&nbsp;983,000&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;naphtha,</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">336,000&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;liquefied&nbsp;petroleum&nbsp;gas;&nbsp;128,000&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;sulfur&nbsp;byproduct,</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">75,000&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;Mixing&nbsp;alcohol&nbsp;and&nbsp;107,000&nbsp;tons&nbsp;of&nbsp;ammonium&nbsp;sulfate.&nbsp;The&nbsp;total&nbsp;investment&nbsp;is&nbsp;estimated&nbsp;RMB&nbsp;55&nbsp;billion,&nbsp;planning&nbsp;to&nbsp;put&nbsp;into&nbsp;operation&nbsp;in&nbsp;2016.</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513843f87600e2', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/shnm_1.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ba9589700ba', '', '2015-12-01 11:50:03', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">As&nbsp;the&nbsp;core&nbsp;technology&nbsp;provider,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">provided&nbsp;oil&nbsp;and&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;processing&nbsp;technology&nbsp;licensing&nbsp;and&nbsp;technology&nbsp;package.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Synfuels&nbsp;China</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">&nbsp;as&nbsp;hospital&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;undertook&nbsp;Shenhua&nbsp;Ningxia&nbsp;Coal&nbsp;Group&nbsp;4&nbsp;million&nbsp;coal&nbsp;indirect&nbsp;liquefaction&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;project&rsquo;s&nbsp;technology&nbsp;package&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;device&nbsp;and&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;device,&nbsp;synthesis&nbsp;of&nbsp;water&nbsp;treatment&nbsp;units&nbsp;and&nbsp;low&nbsp;oil&nbsp;washing&nbsp;unit&nbsp;(i.e.,&nbsp;oil&nbsp;processing&nbsp;unit&nbsp;II&nbsp;region),&nbsp;oxygen&nbsp;and&nbsp;water&nbsp;purification&nbsp;stations&nbsp;and&nbsp;liquid&nbsp;condensate&nbsp;tank&nbsp;intermediate&nbsp;feedstock&nbsp;overall&nbsp;design,&nbsp;basic&nbsp;design,&nbsp;detailed&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;and&nbsp;procurement&nbsp;services&nbsp;work&nbsp;(i.e.&nbsp;E&nbsp;+&nbsp;PS&nbsp;mode).</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513843f87600e2', '2', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515d4e5dc003d2', '煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室首届理事会在北京召开', '2015-12-01 19:29:55', '2009年12月27日，“煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室” 第一届理事会第一次会议在北京召开。国家发展和改革委员会高技术司创新能力建设处袁军处长、中科院高技术研究与发展局刘桂菊副局长、中科院计划财务局潘锋副局长、中国石油和化学工业协会胡迁林副秘书长以及工程实验室各理事单位的理事和代表出席了本次会议。我公司李永旺总经理、郑大为执行总裁、曹立仁总工、相宏伟副总经理、赵璐琦副总经理、杨勇主任和郝栩副主任等参加了此次会议。\r\n \r\n  “煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室” 第一次理事会会议由实验室依托单位中科院山西煤化所组织召开，由中科合成油技术有限公司组织承办，山西煤化所副所长蔡榕主持了会议。袁军处长宣读了国家发展和改革委员会办公厅关于煤炭间接液化国家工程实验室项目的复函，潘锋副局长介绍了首届理事会单位和理事会成员名单，并颁发聘书；与会人员一致鼓掌选举通过由中科院山西煤化所王建国所长担任本届理事会理事长。之后，王建国理事长组织与会人员讨论通过了理事会章程、理事会成员名单和技术委员会成员名单，同时聘任李永旺研究员担任工程实验室主任、曹立仁研究员担任总工、相宏伟研究员、杨勇研究员和郝栩研究员担任副主任。', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137b808c50048', '1', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/IMG_1107(1).jpg', '2009-12-27');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515bae29fa00bc', 'Sustainable development', '2015-12-01 11:55:19', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 5.25pt; margin-left: 5.25pt; line-height: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast\">Starting the innovation and technological integration by using coal technology, improving energy utilization efficiency, further researching and developing sustainable biomass to meet the increasing energy demands of the society is the efforts made by SYNFUELS for sustainable development. It is also our direction of continuous dedication. The technique and technology researched and developed by the company enable oil products to be utilized cleanly and highly efficiently. Tests have shown that it reached European V standards. It is truly free of sulfur, choline orarenes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">The basic requirements on energy in future social development are safety, economy, efficiency and clean utilization. SYNFUELS China Co., Ltd. has made innovative research and development in indirect production of oil and chemicals from coal according to the technological development trend of indirect coal liquidation and the good connecting utilizationcharacteristics of Fischer-Tropsch synthesis and future biomass (especially residues). Technical option research has been done on the aspects of indirect liquidation of coal, low-temperature dry distillation, grading liquidation, gas turbine power generation and other energy integrating process to improve overall energy conversion and utilization rate. At the same time, R&amp;D and demonstrative projects of biomass gasification are combined to actively promote utilization of Fischer-Tropsch technology in biomass.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e85137806001513846ca3600e4', '1', '1', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ca8d7ae014c', 'In 2002', '2015-12-01 16:29:07', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">Through systematic R&amp;D, construction and long-term stable operation of synthetic oil middle test platform were realized and batch samples of high quality diesel were produced.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', 'From Year of 2002-2003', '402881e851378060015137adf0d20018', '4', '1', '', '', '');
