t-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">The&nbsp;R&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;D&nbsp;Department&nbsp;consists&nbsp;of&nbsp;three&nbsp;functional&nbsp;test&nbsp;centers:&nbsp;coal&nbsp;quality&nbsp;analysis&nbsp;and&nbsp;testing&nbsp;center,&nbsp;product&nbsp;analysis&nbsp;and&nbsp;testing&nbsp;center,&nbsp;and&nbsp;environmental&nbsp;monitoring&nbsp;center,&nbsp;with&nbsp;76&nbsp;sets&nbsp;of&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;total&nbsp;value&nbsp;of&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;RMB&nbsp;50&nbsp;million,&nbsp;among&nbsp;which&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;70%&nbsp;belong&nbsp;to&nbsp;international&nbsp;advanced&nbsp;and&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;first-class&nbsp;equipment.&nbsp;The&nbsp;company&nbsp;got&nbsp;CMA&nbsp;accreditation&nbsp;measurement&nbsp;certificate&nbsp;in&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2011,&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;qualified&nbsp;to&nbsp;carry&nbsp;out&nbsp;the&nbsp;relevant&nbsp;analytical&nbsp;testing&nbsp;and&nbsp;technical&nbsp;development.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Technology&nbsp;Department&nbsp;is&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;operation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Yitai&nbsp;and&nbsp;Lu&rsquo;an&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;plants&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;technical&nbsp;support&nbsp;work,&nbsp;organizes&nbsp;and&nbsp;implements&nbsp;the&nbsp;&ldquo;safe,&nbsp;stable,&nbsp;long,&nbsp;full&nbsp;and&nbsp;excellent&rdquo;&nbsp;operation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;plants,&nbsp;designs&nbsp;preparation&nbsp;of&nbsp;transformation,&nbsp;obtains&nbsp;operational&nbsp;data&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;reliable&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;data,&nbsp;monitors&nbsp;the&nbsp;production&nbsp;and&nbsp;run&nbsp;of&nbsp;equipments,&nbsp;optimizes&nbsp;processes&nbsp;and&nbsp;equipment,&nbsp;and&nbsp;maintains&nbsp;a&nbsp;long-term&nbsp;stable&nbsp;operation.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">Production&nbsp;Department&nbsp;is&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;enlargement&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;high-tech&nbsp;laboratory&nbsp;techniques,&nbsp;ensures&nbsp;the&nbsp;drive,&nbsp;operation,&nbsp;maintenance,&nbsp;transformation&nbsp;and&nbsp;construction&nbsp;guardianship&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;pilot&nbsp;platform,&nbsp;collects&nbsp;data&nbsp;during&nbsp;operation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;testing&nbsp;project,&nbsp;describes&nbsp;and&nbsp;concludes&nbsp;the&nbsp;operational&nbsp;status&nbsp;in&nbsp;details,&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;provides&nbsp;commercialization&nbsp;device&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;firsthand&nbsp;process&nbsp;operating&nbsp;parameters&nbsp;and&nbsp;operating&nbsp;methods.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋; font-size:14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; \">To&nbsp;meet&nbsp;the&nbsp;demands&nbsp;for&nbsp;catalyst&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;start&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;million-ton&nbsp;coal-oil&nbsp;commercial&nbsp;demonstration&nbsp;project,&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;started&nbsp;the&nbsp;construction&nbsp;of&nbsp;48,000&nbsp;tons/year&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal&nbsp;liquefaction&nbsp;catalyst&nbsp;and&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;support&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;project&nbsp;(the&nbsp;first&nbsp;phase&nbsp;of&nbsp;0.12&nbsp;million&nbsp;tons/year)&nbsp;in&nbsp;2013,&nbsp;and&nbsp;completed&nbsp;and&nbsp;put&nbsp;into&nbsp;stand-alone&nbsp;test&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;2014.&nbsp;The&nbsp;completion&nbsp;and&nbsp;implementation&nbsp;of&nbsp;this&nbsp;project&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;very&nbsp;important&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;significance&nbsp;to&nbsp;enhance&nbsp;the&nbsp;technology&nbsp;industry&nbsp;support&nbsp;capability&nbsp;of&nbsp;Synfuels&nbsp;China&nbsp;Technology&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;to&nbsp;improve&nbsp;local&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;level,&nbsp;to&nbsp;upgrade&nbsp;the&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;structure,&nbsp;to&nbsp;promote&nbsp;the&nbsp;sustainable&nbsp;and&nbsp;healthy&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;coal&nbsp;chemical&nbsp;industry.</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '1', '', '402881e851378060015137afb0060022', '2', '2', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `zk_en_content_info` VALUES ('ff808081515b3fc401515ce25b240261', '伊泰精细化学品项目费托反应器吊装成功', '2015-12-01 17:31:57', '2014年8月15日，由中化二建承吊的内蒙古伊泰化工120万吨/年精细化学品项目费托合成反应器吊装成功。\r\n\r\n该设备是中科合成油完全自主研发的首台反应器，由中航黎明锦西化工机械有限公司制造。该项目位于内蒙古杭锦旗独贵塔拉工业园区，其主要产品为高熔点费托合成蜡、环保型低芳溶剂、粘度指数改进剂等精细化学品。\r\n\r\n\r\n2014-8-18 中国煤化网', '1', '', '402881e8513780600151382ef9500071', '2', '1', '', 'http://114.242.195.204:81/upload/files/images/20130509%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E5%A7%94%E4%B9%A6%E8%AE%B0%E9%83%AD%E9%87%91%E9%BE%99%E6%9D%A5%E8%AE%BF2.JPG', '2014-8-15');
